    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, it describes objects managing SNMP agents that use the Agent Extensibility (AgentX) Protocol. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
